seo: 代码扫描,默认规则,语言检测,项目分片,编译选项
seo_en: code scanning,default rules,language detection,project slicing,compilation options
summary: 该插件用于根据传入的URL提供代码扫描的默认参数，并支持多种编程语言和编译选项，同时可以对项目进行分片以提高编译速度。
summary_en: This plugin provides default parameters for code scanning based on the input URL, supports multiple programming languages and compilation options, and can slice projects to improve compilation speed.
